The paper presents an algorithm for searching regular expression matches in compressed text, which involves data structures and efficient complexity bounds. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), and Programming Languages (cs.PL).
